reviews.text: Excellent steak for the price!  Highly recommended!
Good food. Price reasonable

Went here for a quick bite. Here's my review on it.

Quick review: Good waffles, a bit too sweet, pretty expensive, clean, great service.

Long review: 

Food: Good food, but a little over sweet. Liked their waffles a lot. Could use more ingredients, like fruits on top, but pretty good. Salad was decent. 

Environment: Nice and comfortable, but sometimes loud. A little dark at times.

Staff: Staff was great. Regular checks on how we were doing, fast service, polite. Satisfied.

Cleanliness: Clean. No complaints.

Price: Cost me around 82.16 for four dishes in Hong Kong dollars. A bit too expensive.

Verdict: Worth trying. Will come here again if I want desert. 3.5 stars.
Although a long quene always shut me off from wish list, food quality in every course compensates time being used to wait for the seat.
Japanese fast food style steak house
